divs: Sighting Detailshi , well one day i went to the dump, to take pics of the bears. this was on my photos . the very last pic is cropped and magnyfied. about 4 months before this at around 6pm, i was lookin out my kitchen window and a huge ball of brillant light came down speeding toward the north. the disk on these photos is comeing from the north. there are 3 hydro electric dams very close by . i didnt hear it comeing or see it. unfortunately my camera is only 2.0 mega pixels the first 2 pics are the orginals and the last i tryed to get a close up of. let me know if u receive these pics, thank you! k.kilborne
